title: Jesus Christ Superstar [25th Anniversary Reissue]
description:
1998 reissue of the soundtrack from the 1973 Norman Jewison film adaptation of the musical "Jesus Christ Superstar" by Andrew Lloyd Webber and Tim Rice.

Cast:

Jesus Christ - Ted Neeley

Judas Iscariot - Carl Anderson

Mary Magdalene - Yvonne Elliman

Pontius Pilate - Barry Dennen

Caiaphas - Bob Bingham

Simon Zealotes - Larry T. Marshall

King Herod - Joshua Mostel

Annas - Kurt Yaghjian
